# Alembic for Legacy RAG Schema

Use this only when maintaining the older `RAG/src` SQL schema.

From `RAG/src/models/db_schemas/nutrition_rag`:

```bash
cp alembic.example.ini alembic.ini
```

Set `sqlalchemy.url` in `alembic.ini`, then run migrations:

```bash
alembic revision --autogenerate -m "Describe schema change"
alembic upgrade head
```

The current `RAG/app` service does not need these migrations when it runs with the default Qdrant vector store.
